<div class="tab-pages">
<div id="pl-459"><div class="panel-grid" id="pg-459-0" ><div class="panel-row-style-tab-page tab-page panel-row-style" ><div class="panel-grid-cell" id="pgc-459-0-0" ><div class="so-panel widget widget_black-studio-tinymce widget_black_studio_tinymce panel-first-child panel-last-child" id="panel-459-0-0-0"><div class="textwidget"><h2>Career Opportunities</h2>
<p>As Western NY's leading IT Service Provider, we place the highest priority in locating and hiring only the finest system professionals available.</p>
<p>There are many career opportunities at PCI. We have a constant demand for top technical professionals to fill openings both in our Service &amp; Support and Core Client Partnership IT Service Groups. We are seeking qualified system professionals who are self-motivated, career minded, personable, and well-organized to work with our Core Clients.</p>
<p><a class="view-more-link" href="/contact">Contact Us &gt;</a></p>
</div></div></div><div class="panel-grid-cell" id="pgc-459-0-1" ><div class="so-panel widget widget_black-studio-tinymce widget_black_studio_tinymce panel-first-child panel-last-child" id="panel-459-0-1-0"><div class="textwidget"><p><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-715" src="http://pciconnected.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/02/careers@2x1.png" alt="careers@2x" width="643" height="656" /></p>
</div></div></div></div></div><div class="panel-grid" id="pg-459-1" ><div class="panel-row-style-tab-page tab-page panel-row-style" ><div class="panel-grid-cell" id="pgc-459-1-0" ><div class="so-panel widget widget_black-studio-tinymce widget_black_studio_tinymce panel-first-child panel-last-child" id="panel-459-1-0-0"><div class="textwidget"><h2>Career Opportunities</h2>
<p><strong>Do you have experience in one or more of the following areas?</strong></p>
<p>+ IT Project Managers<br />
+ Network Support Specialists<br />
+ Network Systems Integrators<br />
+ Desktop Integrators &amp; Support Specialists<br />
+ Help Desk Technical Support Specialists<br />
+ Marketing Sales Associates</p>
<p>Qualified applicants should possess excellent verbal &amp; written communication, interpersonal and problem solving skills. Must have the ability to prioritize tasks and make informed decisions, have a good understanding of customer service and work effectively within a team. Must demonstrate flexibility in a changing environment.</p>
<p>PCI is an equal opportunity employer offering competitive salaries, comprehensive benefits including medical, dental, 401K, technical training, employee discount purchase program and much more.</p>
<p>To find out more about joining the PCI Team, send your resume, references and salary history to: PCI, HR Dept. 703 Washington Street Buffalo, NY 14203 or attach your resume, references and salary history to: <a href="mailto:Careers@PCIbuf.com">Careers@PCIbuf.com</a></p>
</div></div></div></div></div></div></div>


